---
const year = new Date().getFullYear();
---

<footer class="mt-24 bg-ink text-white">
  <div class="mx-auto grid max-w-7xl gap-10 px-4 py-12 sm:px-6 md:grid-cols-[1fr_0.7fr] lg:px-8">
    <div>
      <p class="font-serif text-3xl font-bold leading-none">Writing systems, agents, and infrastructure notes.</p>
      <p class="mt-4 max-w-2xl text-sm leading-6 text-white/65">
        A technical archive for RAG systems, AI agents, backend practice, DevTools, VPS operations, and long-running engineering notes.
      </p>
    </div>
    <div class="font-mono text-xs uppercase tracking-[0.12em] text-white/55 md:text-right">
      <p>Built with Astro + Markdown</p>
      <p class="mt-2">© {year} Fang Systems</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</footer>
